## Animation rules

Good places for `animationType`:

- `fadeInDown` â€” section heading groups
- `fadeInLeft` / `fadeInRight` â€” major columns
- `scaleOnHover` â€” cards, buttons, link wrappers

Bad places (do not animate):

- every paragraph
- every nested group
- every column
- icons in isolation

Use `animateOnScroll:true` alongside `fadeIn*` types.

---

## Custom class rules

Only use `ollieCustomClasses` values confirmed in context.md (populated from `dhali-classes.css` on first run).

If a class is not listed in context.md, read `assets/css/dhali-classes.css` before using it, then cache the full list in context.md.

Do not invent class names. Do not add custom CSS without user approval.

---

## Dhali pattern rules

- PHP file returns `array(...)`.
- `categories` must include `dhali-web-development` **plus** one core-style category: `header`, `footer`, `navigation`, `card`, `query`, `template-part`, `text`, `columns`, `gallery`, `call-to-action`.
- Prefer core blocks unless the project already uses a plugin block for the same purpose.
- Prefer theme preset tokens over hardcoded values.
- Match project indentation and content string style.
- Do not use WordPress 7.0-only APIs without confirming readiness from context.md.

---

## WordPress 7.0 awareness (use only when context.md confirms support)

- **Iframed editor**: avoid CSS/JS that depends on parent admin DOM; prefer block supports and enqueued editor-safe assets.
- **Block API v3+**: use only when `apiVersion` is already v3 in project files.
- **Pattern Overrides / contentOnly**: add `"role":"content"` to editable block.json attributes only after confirming project conventions.
- **Interactivity API**: prefer `watch()` + server-populated `state.url`; avoid `state.navigation` assumptions.
- **DataViews/DataForms**: prefer over `WP_List_Table` for admin UI in WP 7 projects.
- **PHP-only block registration**: consider `supports.autoRegister` + render callback for server-rendered WP 7-only blocks.

WP 7 audit grep (run only when a compatibility pass is requested):

```bash
grep -R "apiVersion\|block_bindings\|metadata.bindings\|register_block_bindings_source\|wp_interactivity\|data-wp-\|state.navigation\|add_meta_box\|WP_List_Table\|register_block_type\|autoRegister\|contentOnly\|role.*content\|ollieCustomClasses" wp-content/themes wp-content/plugins 2>/dev/null
```

